*******************************
Quick install instructions
*******************************

Backup current installation.
Extract contents from "orbicon-2.2.3.zip" and overwrite existing files.


**********************************
Update Details for version 2.2.3
**********************************
25/03/2009

- added support for subdirectory synchronization
- fixed problem with db dump not being deleted on remote host after synchronization
- added pagination to database viewer

-- SQL for 2.2.3 ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
INSERT INTO `orbicon_settings` (`setting`, `value`) VALUES ('sync_dirs', '');

