**********************************
Update Details for version 2.1.5
**********************************
25/10/2007

- added option in settings for date listing in Video gallery
- 6 new modules for Estates
- new module Top Search Keywords
- IRI implementation
- speed optimizations
- added failsafe SQL for ISO-8859-1 URLs that will work in most situations
- added watermark_image() method to Venus
- replaced build_url() method with url() function which assumes properly set mod_rewrite rules
- Mercury and Venus classes are more modular now
- improvements to image gallery
- fixed installed languages not being available in translation import list
- fixed date format setting not being included into database for newly installed languages
- cleanup process starts up more often now and reports size of obsolete files removed
- altering default language in database will now consider installed modules
- fixed identical video titles
- Peoplering search now uses GET instead of POST method
- fixed Peoplering search pagination
- fixed Peoplering promotional messages
- empty names for categories in databases are no longer possible
- fixed uploading files from text database into images and documents
- fixed duplicate categories in text, image and document databases
- new column names will be stripped of extra whitespace
- fixed permalink conflict check when columns were overriden with module content
- Who's here won't remember logged out users
- statistics and site settings changes should be visible immediately
- removed column redirection which caused an infinite loop
- fixed custom titles saved by sessions

-- SQL for 2.1.5 ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
INSERT INTO `orbicon_settings` (`setting`, `value`) VALUES ('video_gallery_show_date', '1');
ALTER TABLE `pring_promo` ADD `contact_id` int(11) NOT NULL default '0';
ALTER TABLE `mercury_categories` ADD `owner_id` int(11) NOT NULL default '0';
ALTER TABLE `venus_categories` ADD `owner_id` int(11) NOT NULL default '0';

