- fixed non-standard file extensions in MagpieRSS
- better installation feedback
- fixed pagination in galleries
- improved video gallery module
- fixed problem with all images uploaded after the first one being put into unsorted category
- fixed redirection problem in Rich Text Editor
- JavaScript size improvements
- added YUI lightbox to 3rd-party resources and made it available in image gallery

