**********************************
Update Details for version 2.1.3
**********************************
10/10/2007

- inword search algorithm is now optional
- added internal search engine statistics and proper settings
- major updates to Estate, Peoplering and Infocenter modules
- column contents can now be overridden with module content
- fixed full screen player mode not working in video gallery
- directories won't be listed in Layout editor any more
- updated YUI to version 2.3.1
- added global helper JavaScript functions: $() for getting elements and redirect() for redirecting
- modules without menu icon will display default application icon
- effects library in orbicon.effects.js is now globally accessible and is not restricted only for backend
- backend GUI improvements
- banner management improvements
- added now() and current_timestamp() methods to $dbc
- documentation update
- new method add_feed_link() for adding custom RSS / RDF feeds to column pages
- JavaScript size improvements
- fixed search not working in Documents and Images database pickers
- added checker for unanswered question, so that user can't send mail without answer
- fixed broken layout on columns
- changed mail body look

-- SQL for 2.1.3 ------------------------------------------------------------------------------

INSERT INTO `orbicon_settings` (`setting`, `value`) VALUES ('override_module', '');
INSERT INTO `orbicon_settings` (`setting`, `value`) VALUES ('stats_attila', '1');
INSERT INTO `orbicon_settings` (`setting`, `value`) VALUES ('inword_search', '1');
ALTER TABLE `orbx_mod_ic_stat` ADD `vid` BIGINT(20) NOT NULL ;

**********************************
Update Details for version 2.1.2
**********************************
02/10/2007

- Attila search engine now supports searching through contents of PDF, DOC, RDF, XML, LOG, RTF, C, CPP, H, CS, CFM, PHPS and TXT files
- new FLV and MP3 Flash players
- images and files can now be replaced with Java uploader
- added new statistics type - hourly activity
- introduced new module Column inspector which identifies common errors in column administration
- introduced new module Backup for cron
- fixed JavaScript problem with IE and get_permalink_exists
- fixed Infobox close button not showing up on IE
- fixed problems with registration form logic
- remove_utf8bom() now supports all UTF BOMS (UTF-8, UTF-16 Big Endian, UTF-16 Little Endian, UTF-32 Big Endian, UTF-32 Little Endian, SCSU, UTF-7 (38 2D), UTF-7 (38), UTF-7 (39), UTF-7 (2B), UTF-7 (2F), UTF-EBCDIC, BOCU-1)
- fixed SQL limitations in statistics
- fixed typo in Send2Friend module
- SEO improvements
- test_form() method rewritten to more modular form
- written better MySQL algorithm for fetching chart data [HPBInvest]
- fixed double date entry bug
- modified data type of table orbx_mod_invest_stock
- redesigned concept of chart layout
- added client side chart switching
- send notification bug fix, added trim whitespace to mail addresses
- added date column to backend of Infocentar question overview
- added trim whitespace to forms in email fields
- news and columns will redirect properly if forcefully loaded
- implemented support for X-LIGHTTPD-send-file header
- CAPTCHA verification is now optional
- fixed icons not showing in backend
- implemented database connection error screen
- fixed column type being ignored during column creation
- HTML minification is now optional
- fixed display order for image, video and download gallery
- all statistics are now optional
- set mode 'optional' for send to friend, watch question and flag question
- added language check in WHERE clause in Infocentar
- added flag question
- added send to friend
- added watch question
- added answer type
- added un-answered questions
- applied backward compatibility for MySQL function CURRENT_TIMESTAMP()

-- SQL for 2.1.2 ------------------------------------------------------------------------------

ALTER TABLE `orbx_mod_invest_stock` CHANGE date date DATE NOT NULL;
ALTER TABLE `mercury_files` ADD search_index LONGTEXT;
ALTER TABLE `mercury_files` ADD FULLTEXT (`search_index`);
INSERT INTO `orbicon_settings` (`setting`, `value`) VALUES ('stats_sess', '1');
INSERT INTO `orbicon_settings` (`setting`, `value`) VALUES ('stats_ip', '1');
INSERT INTO `orbicon_settings` (`setting`, `value`) VALUES ('stats_content', '1');
INSERT INTO `orbicon_settings` (`setting`, `value`) VALUES ('stats_refer', '1');
INSERT INTO `orbicon_settings` (`setting`, `value`) VALUES ('stats_country', '1');
INSERT INTO `orbicon_settings` (`setting`, `value`) VALUES ('stats_keyword', '1');
INSERT INTO `orbicon_settings` (`setting`, `value`) VALUES ('stats_hourly', '1');

-- watch / flag / send2f
-- ---------------------
ALTER TABLE `orbx_mod_ic_settings` ADD `watch_question` TINYINT( 1 ) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0', ADD `flag_question` TINYINT( 1 ) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0', ADD `send_friend` TINYINT( 1 ) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0';

-- answer type
-- -----------
 ALTER TABLE `orbx_mod_ic_settings` ADD `answer_type` TINYINT( 1 ) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0';

-- un-answered questions
-- ----------------------
 ALTER TABLE `orbx_mod_ic_settings` ADD `unanswered ` TINYINT( 1 ) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0';

