**********************************
Update Details for version 2.1
**********************************
06/09/2007

- filesystem improvements
- improved memory and speed performance for SQL requests
- updated YUI to version 2.3.0
- implemented PHPMailer to handle all emails
- fixed double forward slashes for some rare cases in synchronization
- fixed polls display logic
- cached pages should now return proper server status codes instead of always returning "200 OK"
- date format from settings now has a global, language-dependent, effect
- statistics will ignore users from local network coming into production environment
- added option to select all categories or a single one as a source for latest news entry module
- added full screen mode to Rich-Text editor. Keyboard shortcut CTRL+F
- fixed RegEx for Rich-Text editor character count in Internet Explorer
- HTML templates will now be scanned and updated for local links during synchronization
- parent columns will now be visible in Zone list
- added DB shortcut key to frontend box menus
- fixed subcolumns in second and on deeper levels not being removed when their parent columns were deleted
- fixed wrong redirection in File Uploader when requested from outside
- added input size restrictions for some settings
- tag cloud better algorithm
- added security check for zero value in invest
- translated labels inside forms
- added category sorting in infocenter
- pinging the system returns "200 OK" message

-- SQL for 2.1 ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
ALTER TABLE `orbx_mod_ic_category` ADD `sortnum` INT( 4 ) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0';
ALTER TABLE `orbicon_forms` ADD `msg_type` TINYINT(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0';
INSERT INTO `orbicon_settings` (`setting`, `value`) VALUES ('show_last_news_from', '');
